{"tid":2056488,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍是否就係法西斯主義者而不自知？","createTime":"2020-06-08T17:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T00:25:58.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea04479e95289c6fdc1c7730835a8c25eee44e93","tid":2056488,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"法西斯主義者認為，自由民主已經過時，並認為在一個極權主義的一黨制國家中完全動員社會是必要的，以使國家為武裝衝突做好準備並有效應對經濟困難。這樣一個國家由一個強大的領導者&mdash;&mdash;如獨裁者和由執政的法西斯黨成員組成的軍事政府&mdash;&mdash;領導，以建立民族團結，維護一個穩定有序的社會。法西斯主義拒絕斷言暴力本質上是消極的，並將政治暴力，戰爭和帝國主義視為可以實現民族復興的手段。法西斯主義者主張混合經濟，其主要目標是通過保護主義和干涉主義的經濟政策實現自給自足（國家經濟自給自足）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B9%2589&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19qFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=dc4e7b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89</a>"},{"pid":"203dcf08ed98b8d4d8f98939fc32b8699ef642b9","tid":2056488,"uid":315780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯，根本每個藍屍都係低配版嘅希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12faca0fa64a511cf367c88a60d5324634ca5b2","tid":2056488,"uid":86504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"同小粉紅一樣<br />\n以為自己係根正苗紅社會主義接班人<br />\n點知比YAVT測試一test<br />\n原來全撚部係納粹主義接班人<br />\n做哂蕭峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce2fec8ded7efb533154701d4db47b8b590a2e8","tid":2056488,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e12faca0fa64a511cf367c88a60d5324634ca5b2","tid":2056488,"uid":86504,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"同小粉紅一樣<br />\n以為自己